唔熟就問隔離個處長」，指即使法案涉公共開支，只要政府支持，都可以改由政府推動。"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"又幾好戲喎.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:50:20.000Z","msg":"左右互搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feff165b78592379365ba5ba9b811df51f9dd2b5","tid":2430792,"uid":367101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74e4c95a6c035b0fa81425962e4f4996cb4b212c","tid":2430792,"uid":81273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:47:16.000Z","msg":"做左副局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有兩個何啟明㗎"},{"pid":"416a165f958d09a8943e82e4321bc7abdd141d58","tid":2430792,"uid":53959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6882e0d3e2d0d2d54b710a57ccc70afd4e0686ec","tid":2430792,"uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"86d05b11e9eed6a486baff7dd62fab3c6e003e39","tid":2430792,"uid":50740,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:49:23.000Z","msg":"何啟明做醜人,方便其他人cosplay反對派"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:51:20.000Z","msg":"姐系卅幾年來一直有班人cosplay反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83e758162f0da2f4f15da54e4efc2334fa4694a","tid":2430792,"uid":32588,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6882e0d3e2d0d2d54b710a57ccc70afd4e0686ec","tid":2430792,"uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"86d05b11e9eed6a486baff7dd62fab3c6e003e39","tid":2430792,"uid":50740,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTim