諷刺何：「局長對香港市民好有信心，年幾唔做野都冇問題，都開到飯。」，又直斥何「人嚟㗎？」。郭指即使失業人士擁有資產，也總不可能賣樓抵債，或變賣其他資產生活，失業市民也未必希望一次過花光積蓄，因為市民儲錢是希望向上流動，但政府的態度如同要市民向下流動。<br />\n<br />\n委員會主席、同為工聯會的陸頌雄則指社會保障體系是治國安邦的大問題，質疑局方有沒有真正理會過市民的感受、真正理解中央政府的精神。何啟明則回應指，內地處理的是「絕對貧窮」，與香港「相對貧窮」的計算方法不同。<br />\n<br />\n何啟明並非首次在會上被黨友狠批，在上月18日的立法會人力事務委員會會議中，陸頌雄提交私人條例草案，要求將最低工資的檢討周期由每兩年改為一年一次。議員麥美娟指，該私人草案不涉及政府公帑，看不到政策上有不可行的地方。何啟明卻稱政府政策並非一個人決定，當立法會根據機制諮詢當局，局方才會詳細研究法案對於公共開支、政府運作及政策構成的影響，屆時會正式向立法會確認。麥美娟隨即炮轟，「即係你(何啟明)耍我哋(議員)呀依家，唔答呀？開呢個會嚟做咩？開呢個會之前唔係諗咗會唔會支持嘅咩？」，又著何「唔熟就問隔離個處長」，指即使法案涉公共開支，只要政府支持，都可以改由政府推動。"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"又幾好戲喎.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:18:24.000Z","msg":"各位唔做嘢奶共<br />\n何明有人話佢會做嘢<br />\n似兩隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爭骨頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a8d9ba4b683b6c8b9c14d2a96d157c6d4bf5ad5","tid":2430792,"uid":369075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:21:16.000Z","msg":"：喂聽日你做反派<br />\n：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c3439c7385b43502dfc08cae709f040d71c18b","tid":2430792,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:26:38.000Z","msg":"tvb肥皂劇lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呃邊個"},{"pid":"9dcf81c1690d93e15db17e180109ebb72ad1443b","tid":2430792,"uid":273723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:30:16.000Z","msg":"轉個頭咪又係投贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢D咪忠誠反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9aa183746441d3e2b376717d9f1b70cbb2bfb32","tid":2430792,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"飽漢不知飢漢飢"},{"pid":"6b0809bae44b8763418e64f9ed6f058994d26051","tid":2430792,"uid":114193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f146e17e0a86d5cfc7d7166ce26dfe0f9f7dd647","tid":2430792,"uid":141668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0879863832713abbb32a5481b6ac85a6055e2ac2","tid":2430792,"uid":170812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:33:36.000Z","msg":"成班都係忠誠廢物"},{"pid":"c2443f0c7bdf365891a05b6006b336eed71432f8","tid":2430792,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:34:45.000Z","msg":"工聯會咪又係賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2f0fa161dd6c91b2c820170fbeb73ae6fe1f79","tid":2430792,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/BlankBoringGuernseycow-mobile.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FBlankBoringGuernseycow-mobile.jpg&h=9111be1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bbc23917285f0e5c5f183033c7055bcffa37ec6","tid":2430792,"uid":253223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:36:09.000Z","msg":"忠誠既廢物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\